Patch Set 6: Code-Review-1

Do we think there will be a case where glanceclient isn't installed and this module is called? I think in such cases the API should fail to start in the first place rather than a lazy exception on not finding the client.

In my conversation with Tom, I mentioned that this file would be deleted as part of the Glare v1 changes. The logic is planned to be moved to different modules.
